# LegacyCraft DevKit - field mappings (SRG format)
# Format: FD: <obfClass>/<obfField> <deobfClass>/<deobfField>
#
# Empty for now. Field mappings require knowing both the owner class and
# the semantic role of the field; for most fields, that role is not
# unambiguous from bytecode alone, so they are omitted on purpose. Add
# entries here as their meaning is verified.
